<div class="nha-container"><div class="nha-row"><div class="nha-gr-12 nha-gr-6@md nha-push-6@md"><div class="nha-large-story-spotlight-content"><h2 class="nha-section-heading">Spotlight: Detroit Merit Earns “A” Grade in Michigan’s Best Public Elementary Schools</h2>
